sk the dev agent may over-engineer or create unnecessary code changes. The dev notes section explicitly calls out \"do NOT rewrite\" for existing components.\n- **Observation:** This is the last story in Epic 5 and the last story in the sprint. No downstream dependencies."}],"totalDurationMs":168501,"totalTokens":72393,"totalToolUseCount":40,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":255,"cache_read_input_tokens":71575,"output_tokens":562,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":255},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
